Aku membicarakan invasi istana!

154
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:06,339
"Invasi istana"

155
00:11:07,339 --> 00:11:08,670
Tentara Qing ada di sini,

156
00:11:08,809 --> 00:11:11,339
dan para diplomat negara berpengaruh mengawasi kita.

157
00:11:11,479 --> 00:11:13,709
Jadi, tidak mungkin mereka menginvasi istana.

158
00:11:15,579 --> 00:11:17,349
Bisa-bisanya kamu begitu tenang?

159
